盾。很多角色复刻早，一些却复刻晚，主要就是受社区舆论和KPI影响，用出皮肤皮肤的方式顶替复刻过早的角色同时复刻老角色。或者即使复刻晚了但给老角色出皮肤也可以安抚厨子。即使他们有抱怨，社区的另一部分人估计会反对。搞笑，不重视角色给你出那么多皮肤，我们喜欢的角色现在还没出多少呢。"},"attached_info":"CkAI99HQzsbpguJzEAMaCTExMTYzMDEyMyD6r6m5BjAAOFVAFnIKMzI2NzkxMDc4N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"18 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-cfbc28518308f3ecb928e2decd3ffe01_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"23_1730982379.995963","card_id":"Q_2889616645","target":{"id":2889616645,"title":"为什么现在的孩子会沉迷手机？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/2889616645","type":"question","created":1730526782,"answer_count":181,"follower_count":290,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2034616,2133077,2733720],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"孩子周末写作业都要带着手机，怎么都要不回来，又不是要打游戏，就是刷刷小视频，有这么大的吸引力嘛"},"attached_info":"CkEI99HQzsbpguJzEAMaCTExMTU1NDUyOCC+/Ja5BjAAOKICQBdyCjI4ODk2MTY2NDV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"18 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-e7cde30c64dc3b6a0bb65b3e7eacfc7a_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"24_1730982379.996364","card_id":"Q_3409253567","target":{"id":3409253567,"title":"男乒世界第一王楚钦为何连续 5 站比赛遭遇单打败绩，他该如何走出低谷期？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/3409253567","type":"question","created":1730941148,"answer_count":234,"follower_count":304,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[14677,171469,550562,2005723,2097703],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"1、2024年7月31日，巴黎奥运会男单1/16决赛，王楚钦 2-4 负于世界第26的瑞典选手莫雷加德，止步32强，爆出大冷门。 2、2024年9月14日，WTT澳门冠军赛半决赛，王楚钦 1-4 不敌队友林诗栋，无缘决赛。 3、2024年10月1日，WTT中国大满贯男单1/16决赛，王楚钦 1-3 负于世界排名第50的丹麦选手林德，止步32强。 4